enum ButtonVariant {
  Primary = "Primary",
  Secondary = "Secondary",
  Success = "Success",
  Danger = "Danger",
  Warning = "Warning",
  Info = "Info"
}

enum ButtonSizes {
  ExtraSmall = "Xs",
  Small = "Sm",
  Medium = "Md",
  Large = "Lg"
}

enum ButtonType {
  Button = "button",
  Submit = "submit",
  Reset = "reset"
}

enum ButtonOpacity {
  Opacity75 = "Opacity75",
  Opacity50 = "Opacity50",
  Opacity25 = "Opacity25"
}

enum ButtonColors {
  Red = "Red",
  RedLighten = "RedLighten",
  RedDarken = "RedDarken",
  Blue = "Blue",
  BlueLighten = "BlueLighten",
  BlueDarken = "BlueDarken",
  Green = "Green",
  GreenLighten = "GreenLighten",
  GreenDarken = "GreenDarken",
  Yellow = "Yellow",
  YellowLighten = "YellowLighten",
  YellowDarken = "YellowDarken",
  Grey = "Grey",
  GreyLighten = "GreyLighten",
  GreyDarken = "GreyDarken"
}

export { ButtonSizes, ButtonType, ButtonVariant, ButtonOpacity, ButtonColors };
